msgctxt "188_Kiryu"
msgid "So. You're looking for the Florist, right?"
msgstr "Está buscando al Florista, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "200_Takashi"
msgid "Kiryu-san!"
msgstr "¡Kiryu-san!"

msgctxt "212_Takashi"
msgid "That's right. I've got a favor I wanna ask him."
msgstr "Sí, quiero pedirle un favor."

msgctxt "224_Kiryu"
msgid "Hm. I know where to find him, but..."
msgstr "Mmm. Sé dónde encontrarlo, pero..."

msgctxt "236_Takashi"
msgid "If you know, then you have to tell me! Please, it's really\\r\n"\n"important!"
msgstr "¡Si lo sabe, tiene que decírmelo! ¡Por favor, es muy\\r \n"\n"importante!"

msgctxt "260_Kiryu"
msgid "Sorry, I can't tell you."
msgstr "Lo siento, no puedo decírtelo."

msgctxt "272_Takashi"
msgid "Huh? But..."
msgstr "¿Eh? Pero..."

msgctxt "284_Takashi"
msgid "No, I understand. Sorry for putting you in that position,\\r\n"\n"Kiryu-san."
msgstr "No, lo entiendo. Perdón por ponerle en esa tesitura,\\r \n"\n"Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "296_Kiryu"
msgid "All right, I'll take you to him."
msgstr "Está bien, te llevaré con él."

msgctxt "308_Takashi"
msgid "You will!? Thanks a ton, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr "¡¿En serio?! ¡Muchas gracias, Kiryu-san!"

msgctxt "332_Man"
msgid "Kiryu-san!"
msgstr "¡Kiryu-san!"

msgctxt "356_Man"
msgid "Long time no see!"
msgstr "¡Cuánto tiempo sin verle!"

msgctxt "368_Kiryu"
msgid "(Hey, isn't this the Florist's son?)"
msgstr "(Oye, ¿no es el hijo del Florista?)"

msgctxt "380_Kiryu"
msgid "You're Takashi, right?"
msgstr "¿Eres Takashi, verdad?"

msgctxt "392_Takashi"
msgid "That's me!"
msgstr "¡Así es!"

msgctxt "404_Kiryu"
msgid "Hey, good to see you."
msgstr "Ey, qué gusto verte."

msgctxt "416_Kiryu"
msgid "What are you doing hanging around here? Don't tell me you\\r\n"\n"and your girlfriend got in another fight?"
msgstr "¿Qué haces por aquí? No me digas que tú\\r \n"\n"y tu novia tuvieron otra pelea."

msgctxt "428_Takashi"
msgid "No chance. Kyoka and I are sailing smooth. Not a cloud in\\r\n"\n"the sky."
msgstr "Para nada. Kyoka y yo estamos mejor que nunca, todo va\\r \n"\n"sobre ruedas."

msgctxt "440_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, glad to hear it."
msgstr "Je, me alegro mucho."

msgctxt "452_Takashi"
msgid "There <Italic>is</Italic> something I wanted to ask you, though."
msgstr "Aunque sí hay <Italic>algo</Italic> que quería preguntarle."

msgctxt "464_Kiryu"
msgid "What's that?"
msgstr "¿Purgatorio?"

msgctxt "476_Takashi"
msgid "You know that time you helped me out a couple of years ago?\\r\n"\n"We went to that information dealer in the Millennium Tower,\\r\n"\n"remember?"
msgstr "¿Recuerda cuando me ayudó hace un par de años?\\r \n"\n"Fuimos a ver a aquel informante en la Torre Millennium,\\r \n"\n"¿se acuerda?"

msgctxt "488_Kiryu"
msgid "In the Millennium Tower?"
msgstr "¿En la Torre Millennium?"

msgctxt "500_Kiryu"
msgid "(Now that I think about it, the Florist <Italic>was</Italic> shacked up in there for a little while.)"
msgstr "(Pensándolo bien, el Florista <Italic>estuvo</Italic> allí un tiempo.)"

msgctxt "512_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, right. You must be talking about the Florist of Sai."
msgstr "Ah, cierto. Debes estar hablando del Florista de Sai."

msgctxt "524_Takashi"
msgid "That's the one! You wouldn't happen to know where I could\\r\n"\n"find him again, would you?"
msgstr "¡Ese mismo! No sabrá dónde podría\\r\n"\n"encontrarlo de nuevo, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "536_Takashi"
msgid "I tried going back to that same room in the Millennium\\r\n"\n"Tower, but it had been turned into some kinda yakuza office! I could barely believe my eyes!"
msgstr "Intenté volver a esa misma sala en la Torre\\r \n"\n"Millennium, ¡pero la convirtieron en una especie de oficina yakuza! ¡Casi no podía creerlo!"

msgctxt "548_Kiryu"
msgid "What do you need the Florist for?"
msgstr "¿Y para qué necesitas al Florista?"

msgctxt "560_Takashi"
msgid "Well, I've got a favor I wanna ask him."
msgstr "Pues, tengo un favor que pedirle."

msgctxt "572_Kiryu"
msgid "Hm. I know where to find him, but..."
msgstr "Mmm. Sé dónde encontrarlo, pero..."

msgctxt "584_Takashi"
msgid "If you know, then you have to tell me! Please, it's really\\r\n"\n"important!"
msgstr "¡Si lo sabe, tiene que decírmelo! ¡Por favor, es muy\\r \n"\n"importante!"

msgctxt "608_Kiryu"
